What will be the output of the following Python code?
```python
class Animal:
    def speak(self):
        return "Generic Animal Sound"

class Dog(Animal):
    def speak(self):
        return "Woof!"

class Puppy(Dog):
    def speak(self):
        return super().speak() + " (small)"

doggo = Dog()
pup = Puppy()
print(doggo.speak() + " | " + pup.speak())
```
